#~ "dan kad njihovo spokojno bitisanje bi razvejano, kada u njihov kraj zađe "
#~ "zli mag, šireći pustoš i očajanje."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Bjarn, the local mage of the village, was the man who saw best how to "
